sub_title: Co-founder at Rawstraw | Communication Science student at UvA
summary:
Making the planet a better place, one straw at a time. 

I'm a Swedish champion in Young Entrepreneurship 2019, co-founder of a company called Rawstraw and winner of the Swedish Dragon's Den 2021. I'm also currently studying BSc Communication Science at the University of Amsterdam, ranked #1 globally by QS World University Rankings for 6 consecutive years.
